				<para>     - It is the starting point of your algorithm.</para>
				<para> The returned value must be true if your algorithm succeeded.</para>
    			</listitem>
    			<listitem>
    				<methodname>bool check (std::string)</methodname> : <para> This method can be used to check what you need about topological properties of the graph, metric properties on graph elements or anything else.</para>
    			</listitem>
