	    	    				<methodname>DataSet* dataSet </methodname> :<para>This member contains all the parameters needed to run the Algorithm. The class DataSet is a container which allows insertion of values of different types. The inserted data must have a copy-constructor well done. See the section called DataSet for more details.</para>
